    "description": "<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >一切的起源</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >本游戏是广受关注的恐怖游戏《不要害怕》的起源故事。你将扮演一名被困在精神病院的病人，深入探索前作反派角色逐渐丧失理智的过程，目睹一个怪物的诞生。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >过程中，请揭开那些曾经在这里受苦的病人们留下的隐藏故事，理解这座疯人院如何成为滋养恐惧的温床。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >你所遭遇的一切，是真实的恶魔，还是正在吞噬你理智的幻觉？界限将彻底模糊。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3255840/extras/13596519cf3243e73257a33cad5516a4.poster.avif?t=1770624471\" width=1170 height=488 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3255840/extras/13596519cf3243e73257a33cad5516a4.webm?t=1770624471\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >窒息的生存与解谜体验</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >在《不要害怕：精神病院》中，你将体验到经典恐怖游戏的紧张感，同时面对来自黑暗深处的威胁：</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >你的生存工具只有微弱的手电筒和稀缺的电池。管理好你的光芒，因为它不仅是照明工具，更是你对抗恐惧的勇气。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3255840/extras/fe86faa4c6483526b1acda894ec26b61.poster.avif?t=1770624471\" width=556 height=306 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3255840/extras/fe86faa4c6483526b1acda894ec26b61.webm?t=1770624471\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3255840/extras/fe86faa4c6483526b1acda894ec26b61.mp4?t=1770624471\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >另外，你不是待宰的羔羊。使用砍刀和麻醉枪进行自卫，但弹药和机会都极为有限。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >面对一系列与精神疾病、病人故事交织在一起的变态谜题，只有解开它们，你才能找到逃离这座地狱的出路。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3255840/extras/7cdbe6df20219545a859c74cda5f8c66.poster.avif?t=1770624471\" width=556 height=306 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3255840/extras/7cdbe6df20219545a859c74cda5f8c66.webm?t=1770624471\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3255840/extras/7cdbe6df20219545a859c74cda5f8c66.mp4?t=1770624471\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p>",
